<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" 
	      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
    <Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">
        Interactive Features
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
       The following samples demonstrate the usage of interactive features in the Gantt control.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
         <Bold>Built-in Zooming</Bold> - This sample illustrates how to zoom the date-time schedule between year and minute time units.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
         <Bold>Calendar Customization</Bold> - This sample illustrates how to customize the date setting of the schedule calendar of the Gantt control.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
         <Bold>Custom ToolTip</Bold> - This sample illustrates how the custom ToolTip is used in the Gantt control.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
	 <Bold>Custom Zooming</Bold> - This sample illustrates how to enable zooming at the sample level.
    </Paragraph>	
    <Paragraph>
	 <Bold>Highlighting Tasks</Bold> - This sample illustrates how to highlight a specific set of tasks in the Gantt chart area.
    </Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
	 <Bold>Strip Lines</Bold> - This sample illustrates how to place the Strip lines in Gantt Chart Region.
    </Paragraph>

</FlowDocument>
